{"tid":2423180,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"道指瀉逾400點 馬斯克據報遭SEC查","createTime":"2021-02-25T18:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T19:28:49.000Z","uid":121260,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16f0086921acf62a03128d168772168dd0e1f743","tid":2423180,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】美國國庫券孳息率繼續上揚，10年期債息周四曾突破1.5厘關口，升幅達到12個基點。債息急飆令風險資產包括股市及黃金的吸引力下降，美股受壓，道指中段最多曾滑落422點，盤中暫時低位觸及31539點；以科技股為主的納指跌幅曾達到2.8%，低見13217點。<br />\n<br />\n電動車公司特斯拉(Tesla)行政總裁馬斯克(Elon Musk)，據報遭美國證券交易委員會(SEC)調查其在Twitter上有關狗狗幣的貼文，特斯拉股價現時插水超過6%，稍早早跌幅一度達到7.39%。較早時有報道稱，特斯拉Model 3在美國加州的生產線暫時停產，分析認為，停產原因主要由於芯片供應短缺。中國概念電動車股受壓，理想汽車下跌超過10%，小鵬汽車挫近8%，蔚來汽車倒退7%。"},{"pid":"1fb40ba84c84e25cc185de63aded4c3f0ef96810","tid":2423180,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:13:23.000Z","msg":"掃貨!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106043016a895571c37302ac06fd6b0703548834","tid":2423180,"uid":94007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"真科爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21cc37d236e6d00fde731c8be649fd9c2a0409e","tid":2423180,"uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"自從佢屌完啲劵商之後就瘋狂比孌童登搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454f1f0826214e3b4ea959d14ab845e06a56db37","tid":2423180,"uid":375059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21cc37d236e6d00fde731c8be649fd9c2a0409e","tid":2423180,"uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:19:36.000Z","msg":"自從佢屌完啲劵商之後就瘋狂比孌童登搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as